column5: hey all we out this morn for a little fish on quinte (no surprize there huh)and low and behold i was all done with my count at 8:30 am while out there a bud walk over to me and said he was all done at 8am  sad to say my cameras at the bottom of the bay  ,but im sure those who know me here know you'll get no Bull out of me.  taker easy all and tight lines  "OH" no Hawgs just all nice eaters in the 3-5lb range.  Hawg Hunter
Maybe a new camera is in the cards for you at the Fishing Show.....too bad.  Nice quick report though.
Where were you fishing Hawg Hunter?
I'm definitely going to make it out there at least once more before the seasons done.
Hey Hawg  did you get them out where we were monday night when you missed the big one and I followed up with the smaller one  Troy

sad to say yes we did,only wish you lads were with us when it happen,darn things been hitting great in the am but not so good in the pm(thats why i asked you if you lads were staying over) i have people fri/sat/sun and i may be there if we fine out the eyes have not moved west under unsafe ice  .  taker easy  Hawg Hunter
